wiki.summary: “I Don’t Know Why” is the first* song on the original release of Imagine Dragons’ 2017 album "Evolve". Notably, its instrumental and lyrics are moodier than the rest of the LP, with a low synthesizer and lyrics about a “dangerous” love. *The song “Next To Me” was later made the first song on Evolve on digital platforms on February 21, 2018. This re-release of the album makes “I Don’t Know Why” Evolve’s second song on digital platforms, with the original release being unlisted and replaced by the 2018 version. Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: “I Don’t Know Why” is the first* song on the original release of Imagine Dragons’ 2017 album "Evolve". Notably, its instrumental and lyrics are moodier than the rest of the LP, with a low synthesizer and lyrics about a “dangerous” love. *The song “Next To Me” was later made the first song on Evolve on digital platforms on February 21, 2018. This re-release of the album makes “I Don’t Know Why” Evolve’s second song on digital platforms, with the original release being unlisted and replaced by the 2018 version. (The original listing still exists on Spotify, but is difficult to locate without being saved to a user’s Library prior to its unlisting.) Read more on Last.fm.
